==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]]: /ˈuːzəʊ/

===Noun===
'''ouzo''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]; plural'' '''ouzos''')

#(''[[uncountable]]'') An [[anise]]-flavoured [[alcoholic]] drink, popular in Greece; (''[[countable]]'') a glass of ouzo.

